      <dependency task="003" status="not-started">`RagIndexingPipeline.IndexSessionFileAsync` ŌĆö referenced by orchestrator (or upstream call site) when staging files into the session-files index.</dependency>
      <dependency task="004" status="not-started">`ChatSession.UploadedFiles[]` manifest ŌĆö orchestrator reads from `ChatSessionManager` to enumerate active session files.</dependency>
